(Sorry about not noticing your guys attacking Savage. I'll rewrite 
the leaving post. As for the Vulois thing, well I was going to show 
it for another reason, but the Soundwave thing may be better. I'll 
have to weigh between the two.)

Savage

The weapons from the other bots pierced Savage's skin. He let out a 
huge roar. He fell to the ground, and struggled to consiousness. He 
couldn't fly. He started running as fast as he could to his cave.
______________________________________________________________________

Zava

Zava saw that Deemos was fighting someone. She decided to show him 
she was a true player, so she pulled out her blasters and fired on 
the bot(Dollen) in a mad spray.
